cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CR 

This paper is about person re-identification, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category. The paper also involves deep learning and optimization, which are common in machine learning, so cs.MM (Machine Learning) is also likely. The paper proposes a novel approach for feature fusion, which falls under the category of data fusion, so cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possible category. The paper also involves evaluation of the proposed approach, which may fall under the category of performance evaluation, so cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is another possible category. Finally, the paper involves human operator performance, which may fall under the category of human-computer interaction, so cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is another possible category.
